userdoc.notice: This is the main contract for PearlZZ It manages "Loyalty Alliances" - an alliance of brands / businesses It allows for alliances at a local town, city, county, state, country, and global levelsIt manages onboarding of Loyalty Issuer's Loyalty Liability stake to PearlZZIt manages individual customers loyalty walletsIt enables a peer-to-peer trading of loyalty points
